article_id:122,category_name:Updates,title_name:Update Notification,image_path:,message:<div>The update to version 1.2.1 was made available at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1543460400"></span>. An automatic update is scheduled to occur at approximately <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1543546800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Issues fixed:</div><div>The following issues have been fixed.</div><div>・High Midgardsormr&#39;s &quot;Storm Chaser&quot; deals more hits than it should in version 1.2.0.</div><div>・Upgrade animation is unskippable after upgrading an adventurer, weapon, dragon, or wyrmprint once.</div><div>・Some of the skill descriptions corrected to better reflect their actual effects.</div><div><br></div><div>■Notes:</div><div>It may take time for the update information to be reflected in the store.</div><div>Players may not be able to perform the update due to their device&#39;s data cache being full.</div><div>If you are unable to perform the update, restart your device and then attempt the download from the store.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1543460400,update_time1543465118